## Concern A — Banshee tunables → catalog

**Verdict:** PASS — pure refactor, no behavior change.
**Commit:** `46faec1319`

Promoted 7 inline magic numbers from the `banshee_charge` AI branch to
named fields on `TYPES.banshee` in `js/hunt/hunt-enemies.js`:

| Field | Value |
|---|---|
| chargeDuration | 0.8 |
| chargeSpeedMul | 1.8 |
| shriekParticleCount | 16 |
| shriekTrauma | 0.3 |
| shriekFlashAlpha | 0.3 |
| shriekFlashDurationMs | 200 |
| shriekLateralMult | 0.4 |

AI branch reads via `c._typeData.<field>`. Flash color sources from the
existing `accent` (`#a060ff`) field. All 7 substitutions are 1:1 with the
original literals — `node --check` passed; live banshee shriek behaviour
identical pre/post.

